<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="ldiv" id="ldiv">ldiv</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">ldiv_t</span> <span class="kw3">ldiv</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> numerator, <span class="kw4">long</span> denominator <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

测试： adiv_t, div_t, ldiv_t.
ldiv() 函数返回 numerator / denominator的商和余数。ldiv_t定义在cstdlib中并至少有：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     <span class="kw4">long</span> quot<span class="sy4">;</span>  <span class="co1">// 商</span>
     <span class="kw4">long</span> rem<span class="sy4">;</span>   <span class="co1">// 余数</span></pre>
<p>
C++中可以使用div()代替ldiv()，因为它为ldiv()提供了一个重载版本。
</p>

<p>
相关主题： <a href="div" class="wikilink1" title="cn:numeric:c:div">div</a>
</p>

</div>
